format: A tbl_df with with 2930 rows and 82 variables:
title: Housing prices in Ames, Iowa
description:
Description
Data set contains information from the Ames Assessor's Office used in
computing assessed values for individual residential properties sold in
Ames, IA from 2006 to 2010. See here
for detailed variable descriptions.
reference:
De Cock, Dean. "Ames, Iowa: Alternative to the Boston housing data as
an end of semester regression project." Journal of Statistics Education 19.3
(2011).

parameters.Street: Type of road access to property.
parameters.Bsmt.Unf.SF: Unfinished square feet of basement area.
parameters.PID:
Parcel identification number  - can be used with city web site
for parcel review.
parameters.Bedroom.AbvGr:
Bedrooms above grade (does NOT include basement
bedrooms).
parameters.Total.Bsmt.SF: Total square feet of basement area.
parameters.MS.Zoning: Identifies the general zoning classification of the sale.
parameters.Overall.Qual: Rates the overall material and finish of the house.
parameters.Overall.Cond: Rates the overall condition of the house.
parameters.BsmtFin.Type.2: Rating of basement finished area (if multiple types).
parameters.TotRms.AbvGrd: Total rooms above grade (does not include bathrooms).
parameters.Bsmt.Qual: Evaluates the height of the basement.
parameters.Open.Porch.SF: Open porch area in square feet.
parameters.Low.Qual.Fin.SF: Low quality finished square feet (all floors).
parameters.area: Above grade (ground) living area square feet.
parameters.Screen.Porch: Screen porch area in square feet.
parameters.Garage.Cars: Size of garage in car capacity.
parameters.Alley: Type of alley access to property.
parameters.Exter.Qual: Evaluates the quality of the material on the exterior.
parameters.Garage.Area: Size of garage in square feet.
parameters.Bsmt.Exposure: Refers to walkout or garden level walls.
parameters.Exterior.2nd: Exterior covering on house (if more than one material).
parameters.Enclosed.Porch: Enclosed porch area in square feet.
parameters.Bsmt.Cond: Evaluates the general condition of the basement.
parameters.Condition.2:
Proximity to various conditions (if more than one is
present).
parameters.Lot.Frontage: Linear feet of street connected to property.
parameters.Functional:
Home functionality (Assume typical unless deductions are
warranted).
parameters.Wood.Deck.SF: Wood deck area in square feet.
parameters.Misc.Feature: Miscellaneous feature not covered in other categories.
parameters.Year.Remod.Add:
Remodel date (same as construction date if no
remodeling or additions).
parameters.X3Ssn.Porch: Three season porch area in square feet.
parameters.Exter.Cond:
Evaluates the present condition of the material on the
exterior.
parameters.Mas.Vnr.Area: Masonry veneer area in square feet.
parameters.MS.SubClass: Identifies the type of dwelling involved in the sale.
parameters.Neighborhood:
Physical locations within Ames city limits (map
available).
